Package com.explodingbacon.bcnlib.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeThread
    A class that allows us to easily write code that will run in its own separate thread.
    I2C
    A class used for communicating over I2C.
    NetTuner
    A way to tune things using a NetTable
    PIDAutoTuner
    A class that attempts to auto-tune your PID controllers.
    PIDManualTuner
    A way to manually tune PID Loops in a network table (and a GUI that reads/writes from the NetworkTable)
    Timer
    A class that lets you set a timer that will be called once (or every) X seconds.
    Utils
    A Utility class that contains functions that are often used in various parts of robot programming.
